<p>1600 is a factory somewhere in the US, build during the Great Depression. MC&amp;D bought it in early 90s and have been siphoning 1600-1 out of it ever since. They don't actually sell it or 1600-2 - it isn't quite unique enough compared to their other products. Instead, they use 1600-2 as appetizers at their shows and auctions.</p>

